quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  41,30,"Mu by’ukuri ba bandi bavuze bati “Nyagasani wacu ni Allah” hanyuma bagashikama (ku kuri), bazamanukirwa n’abamalayika (mu gihe cyabo cyo gupfa, bababwira bati) “Mwigira ubwoba ndetse n’agahinda, ahubwo nimwakire inkuru nziza y’ijuru mwajyaga musezeranywa”"
  41,31,"“Twebwe turi inshuti zanyu mu buzima bwo ku isi ndetse n’ubwo ku mperuka. Kandi (mu ijuru) muzahabwamo ibyo imitima yanyu izifuza, ndetse murihabwemo ibyo muzasaba byose.”"
  41,32,"(Ibyo) bizaba ari izimano riturutse kuri (Allah) Ubabarira ibyaha, Nyirimpuhwe"
  41,33,"Ni nde wavuga imvugo nziza kurusha wa wundi uhamagarira (abantu) kugana Allah, kandi agakora ibikorwa byiza, nuko akavuga ati “Mu by’ukuri njye ndi umwe mu bicisha bugufi” (Abayisilamu).”"
  41,34,"Kandi igikorwa cyiza n’ikibi ntibishobora kungana. Bityo, inabi (wakorewe) jya uyikosoza ineza; ibyo bizatuma uwo mwari mufitanye urwango aba nk’inshuti yawe magara"
  41,35,"Ariko (ibyo) ntababihabwa usibye ba bandi bihangana, ndetse nta n’undi wabihabwa usibye umunyamahirwe ahambaye"
  41,36,"Kandi Shitani niramuka ishatse kugushuka, ujye wikinga kuri Allah. Mu by’ukuri (Allah) ni We Uwumva bihebuje, Umumenyi uhebuje"
  41,37,"No mu bimenyetso bye (Allah) harimo ijoro n’amanywa, ndetse n’izuba n’ukwezi. Bityo, ntimukubamire izuba cyangwa ukwezi, ahubwo mujye mwubamira Allah We wabiremye, niba koko ari We wenyine mugaragira"
  41,38,"Ariko nibibona (bakanga kugaragira Allah), bamenye ko abari kwa Nyagasani wawe (abamalayika) bamwambaza ijoro n’amanywa, batarambirwa na gato"